{"tid":1593822,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"要抗爭成功，必須十月一日起令警員不斷失去工作能力","createTime":"2019-09-25T08:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T13:43:23.000Z","uid":151057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fafffbc78970dde430dad991f8fcf46a5042f1e2","tid":1593822,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T08:55:43.000Z","msg":"隨住抗爭不斷<br />\n前線每次人數因為濫捕而減少<br />\n相反警員人數三個月來從來減少<br />\n情況持續衹損害抗爭力量<br />\n<br />\n以上行動是否會令運動污名？<br />\n不會，文宣會大力宣傳是由於警察暴行無法法天，反而民間會出現「終於做到野」的良好回應。<br />\n<br />\n以上行動會否令警員加劇酷刑反擊？<br />\n不會，警員之酷刑當市民是昆蟲，待遇比戰犯更惡劣，已差無可差。<br />\n<br />\n注意<br />\n以上立場是不應該攻擊警員。攻擊頭盔或手臂等行為不但是無效，不人道，而且畫面不靚的。<br />\n<br />\n應該快速，乾淨，瞬間令警員失去半年以上工作能力，以最有效率削弱人數。<br />\n<br />\n於衝突現場期間進行會降低人數減少成功率。<br />\n<br />\n如果人數削減可以大於被捕人數，<br />\n運動最終必定會成功。"},{"pid":"817fd1eb35b01a4b50324a806aa756f510865b6a","tid":1593822,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T08:58:36.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"081e90af892867c1d494130e0c7851b43bd58907","tid":1593822,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T08:59:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">國&hearts;際&hearts;戰&hearts;線&hearts;需&hearts;要&hearts;你</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RH29z9Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRH29z9Z.jpg&h=787fa8fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">☆</span>Tg channel在此 <a href=\"http://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9BvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=cfa0731d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twittermansyunzou</a> <span style=\"color: gold;\">☆</span>"},{"pid":"5060d14c3af15bad8d8adeeb6725a32e3ccc5225","tid":1593822,"uid":286564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T13:4